properties.sfomuseum:description: Handwritten letter from Harold M. Bixby to his family, dated Monday, October 16, 1933; on flight from Shanghai to Hong Kong to board a ship to Manila; update on provisional operating contract, description of Executive Yuan; includes description of Swatow [Shantou] area and the flight.
